Package org.openrdf.rio.nquads

Parser and writer for RDF in N-Quads format.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NQuadsParser
    RDF parser implementation for the N-Quads RDF format, extending the Rio N-Triples parser.
    NQuadsParserFactory
    An RDFParserFactory for N-Quads parsers.
    NQuadsWriter
    RDFWriter implementation for the N-Quads RDF format.
    NQuadsWriterFactory
    An RDFWriterFactory for N-Quads writers.

Package org.openrdf.rio.nquads Description

Parser and writer for RDF in N-Quads format. The N-Quads format is defined here .
